sentence.text: In vitro analysis revealed that knockdown of WWOX protein in neuroblastoma cells results in aggregation of TRregulation of presynapse assemblyC6AΔ, TIAF1, amyloid β, and Tau in a sequential manner.

Homozygous null mutation of tumor suppressor negative regulation of Wnt signaling pathway/Wwox gene leads to severe neural diseases, metabolic disorders and early death in the newborns of humans, mice and rats.
